Class ParkingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.AreaLimitedManager
      • com.inrix.sdk.ParkingManager

  • public class ParkingManager
extends AreaLimitedManager
    Manages asynchronous operations about parking lot information.
